00:00:11.164 --> 00:00:15.051
I have a simple question.
You ge jian dan de wen ti.

00:00:15.282 --> 00:00:18.137
What is love?
Shen me shi ai qing?

00:00:18.372 --> 00:00:23.894
Is it a kind of smell or attraction?
Ta shi fou shi yi zhong wei dao, hai shi yin li?

00:00:24.129 --> 00:00:27.824
Starting from the day of my first love,
Cong wo chu lian na tian qi,

00:00:28.012 --> 00:00:31.105
I experienced sweet days,
Xian shi tian mi.

00:00:31.383 --> 00:00:36.062
and then storms.
Ran hou jin jie jiu hui you feng yu.

00:00:37.372 --> 00:00:41.303
Love is like a sunny day with blue sky and white clouds,
Ai jiu xiang lan tian bai yun, qing kong wan li,

00:00:41.537 --> 00:00:44.346
and suddenly turns to a stormy day,
Tu ran bao feng yu.

00:00:44.534 --> 00:00:50.148
nowhere to hide, always unexpected.
Wu chu duo bi, zong shi rang ren shi liao bu ji.

00:00:50.383 --> 00:00:54.363
People in love are like catching a bad cold and coughing,
Ren jiu xiang huang zhong gan mao da zhe pen ti,

00:00:54.550 --> 00:00:57.172
taking a rest after having a fever,
Fa shao yao xiu xi.

00:00:57.402 --> 00:01:04.004
feeling cold and then hot, happy and then sad. They always enjoy it.
Leng re jao ti, huan xi you yu, le ci bu pi.

00:01:10.606 --> 00:01:13.174
I have a giddy question.
Jiao ren tou yun de wen ti.

00:01:14.122 --> 00:01:16.169
What is love?
Shen me jiao ai qing?

00:01:16.869 --> 00:01:23.285
It is so real, yet so doubtful.
Ta shi na me de zhen shi, you hen ke yi.

00:01:23.516 --> 00:01:29.695
I've researched many oaths, like "till the sea dried, stones rotten".
Yan jiu guo xu duo shi yan, hai ku shi lan.

00:01:29.882 --> 00:01:34.748
only discovered that it is fruitless to explain them.
Fa jue yue xiang yao jie shi, yue luan.

00:01:35.919 --> 00:01:39.849
So how long is "forever"? "Forever" can be momentary.
Suo yi shuo yong yuan duo chang, yong yuan duan zan,

00:01:40.036 --> 00:01:42.894
"Forever" can be regrettable.
Yong yuan hen yi han.

00:01:43.126 --> 00:01:48.600
Everyone has its own experience of love.
Mei ge ren you mei ge ren bu tong de ti yan.

00:01:48.841 --> 00:01:52.676
The taste of love, sometimes flying up high, somtimes down,
Na zi wei, shi er zai fei, shi er xia zhui.

00:01:52.862 --> 00:01:55.529
somethings makes one cry.
Shi er you luo lei.

00:01:55.761 --> 00:02:01.990
The touching movie, experience it by yourself, don't say ticket is too expensive.
Dong ren dian ying, zi ji ti hui, bie xian piao tai gui

00:02:03.810 --> 00:02:08.490
Take good wine and coffee as an example. Both are liquid.
Bi ru mei jiu he ka fei, dou shi shui,

00:02:09.566 --> 00:02:15.043
Yet one makes you sober, another one makes you drunk.
Ke yi ge rang ni xing, yi ge rang ni zui.

00:02:15.231 --> 00:02:21.456
Can we take it as an analog of love?
Na me gan qing neng fou yi ci lei tui.

00:02:21.735 --> 00:02:28.942
It can be bland, or leave you stuck and heartbroken.
You de hen ping dan, you de si xin lie fei.

00:02:31.096 --> 00:02:34.839
