Suo yi shuo yong yuan duo chang, yong yuan duan zan,

00:02:35.073 --> 00:02:37.883
"Forever" can be slow.
Yong yuan hen huan man.

00:02:38.116 --> 00:02:43.777
Everyone has its own calculation on love.
Mei ge ren you mei ge ren bu tong de ji suan.

